<bibRefCitation id="EF83B4DAFFBF5723FBE197AD7803078D" author="Emerson, A. E. &amp; Banks, F." box="[1102,1384,1465,1492]" pageId="14" pageNumber="459" pagination="1 - 17" refId="ref8446" refString="Emerson, A. E. &amp; Banks, F. (1957) Five species and one redescription of the Neotropical genus Armitermes Wasmann (Isoptera, Termitidae, Nasutitermitinae). American Museum Novitates, 1841, 1 - 17." type="journal article" year="1957">Emerson &amp; Banks (1957)</bibRefCitation>
